[Name] Wmhdplop
[Summary] Monitors your hard drives
[Description] wmhdplop monitors your hard drives and displays visual information about their activity (read, write, swapin, swapout), and optionally (if hddtemp is running as a daemon), displays their temperature/status.
[License] GNU General Public License version 2
[Homepage] http://hules.free.fr/wmhdplop
